name: Organ Haikus #4
description: By an imaginative leap, the agents of Copy Planet. Ciphers of the universe decodes a poignant message. Transmitting the message like an organ within the cosmos. It is a message sent through the vibrations and rhythmic pulses coursing through our hearts. The universe is sublime, living and conscious, a divine creature whose nature is reflected in human existence. Cooked by collaborating with artist Salafurka.
